content: Quantum Conversations by the Bay (https://quantum.sv/) is an IBM-sponsored "unconference" on quantum computation hosted online on May 27. Come to see some applied category theory (ZX-calculus) in action. Stay to hear about some quantum chemistry on IBM's 53-qubit quantum computer. :) Attendees are welcome to ask questions or give lightning talks afterwards. RSVP on the website to get an invite.
